Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:47.48,Comment,A,0,0,0,,{\pos(796,654)}Shiny Chariot
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:01.62,Default,A,0,0,0,,我要在这里当上魔女
