Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:46.93,Comment,A,0,0,0,,{\pos(716,654)}Terminal
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:50.33,Default,A,0,0,0,,再说了 这地图也太简陋了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:52.33,Default,A,0,0,0,,这样根本看不明白呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:01.93,Default,A,0,0,0,,找到了 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:13.48,Default,A,0,0,0,,好痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:15.82,Default,A,0,0,0,,对...对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.08,0:04:26.55,Default,A,0,0,0,,这是你的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:28.55,Default,A,0,0,0,,你也是新月学园的新生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:30.55,Default,A,0,0,0,,现在要去办开学典礼的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:31.71,Default,A,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:36.13,Default,A,0,0,0,,要独自一个人去魔女的学校 还是有点怕怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:37.26,Default,A,0,0,0,,我是亚可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:37.26,Comment,A,0,0,0,,{\pos(676,654)}Akko
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:40.48,Default,A,0,0,0,,从我六岁时看了闪耀夏莉奥的魔法秀以来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:42.48,Default,A,0,0,0,,就一直梦想成为一位魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.48,0:04:45.06,Default,A,0,0,0,,不如说 这是超越梦想的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:47.68,Default,A,0,0,0,,你也应该认识吧 闪耀夏莉奥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:51.48,Default,A,0,0,0,,瞧 夏莉奥的稀有卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:51.48,Comment,A,0,0,0,,{\pos(736,654)}Rare Card
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:53.48,Default,A,0,0,0,,我的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:55.68,Default,A,0,0,0,,在魔法界里 夏莉奥也非常有影响力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:04:58.97,Default,A,0,0,0,,在我的周围 完全没人喜欢夏莉奥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:02.82,Default,A,0,0,0,,他们总是吐槽我「你在说哪个年代事情」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:05.71,Default,A,0,0,0,,那么厉害的事 夏莉奥以外没人能做到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.71,0:05:07.84,Default,A,0,0,0,,毕竟她连月...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.53,0:05:19.04,Default,A,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:20.73,Default,A,0,0,0,,傀儡魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:22.73,Default,A,0,0,0,,头一次亲眼见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:27.64,Default,A,0,0,0,,乖 乖 到这边来 不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.13,0:05:31.62,Default,A,0,0,0,,眼睛 我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:35.04,Default,A,0,0,0,,等等 这太过分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:37.73,Default,A,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:43.37,Default,A,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字？ 刚才是怎么做到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:48.17,Default,A,0,0,0,,我也邮购了魔法教材 但是完全搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:50.48,Default,A,0,0,0,,都不知道有没有打好基础
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:52.46,Default,A,0,0,0,,不过到了学校里学习之后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:55.64,Default,A,0,0,0,,也不知能不能用出夏莉奥那样的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:00.15,Default,A,0,0,0,,请...请问
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.37,Default,A,0,0,0,,那...那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:07.86,Default,A,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:14.68,Default,A,0,0,0,,讨厌 讨厌 讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:29.88,Default,A,0,0,0,,真是的 那家伙是怎么回事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:37.26,Default,A,0,0,0,,新月学园的校服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.84,0:06:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,春假过得怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,无论去哪里都全是游客 挤死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来在今天开学典礼入学的新生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有一人不是来自魔女家族
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 最近一般人太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,最近因为学校的经营困难的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,说是不得不让非魔女家族入学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:06:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.42,0:07:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,新月学园的品格都被拉低了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,连扫帚都骑不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,骑不了扫帚的魔女 在新月学园的历史里是从未有过的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.95,Default,A,0,0,0,,卡嘉莉 敦子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.95,Comment,A,0,0,0,,{\pos(599,650)}篝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:16.08,Default,A,0,0,0,,是新生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 就是你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:20.06,Default,A,0,0,0,,那...那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:23.97,Default,A,0,0,0,,能快点来就好了 巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,巴士？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:27.60,Default,A,0,0,0,,诶 这里不是巴士站吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这里会有巴士来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.13,0:07:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Tia Fraere
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是扫帚的车站
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,灵脉节点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:40.77,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,654)}Leyline Terminal
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,从这里由灵脉连接着新月学园
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,灵脉从太古时起就运输着魔法的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,乘着这股能量就可以飞到新月学园去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是魔法的高速路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:55.46,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\pos(750,654)}Highway
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.46,0:07:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这是魔女的基础知识哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,要是在开学典礼时迟到的话 会被魔法界永久驱逐的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:18.53,Default,A,0,0,0,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.17,0:08:42.84,Default,l,0,0,0,,哇 已经要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:47.08,Default,L,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:51.08,Default,L,0,0,0,,妈妈和老姐让我带的行李真是太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:51.08,TopLeft,L,0,0,0,,注：「老姐」这里是个人名，不确定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:08:55.75,Default,L,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:02.93,Default,L,0,0,0,,Tia F...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:07.82,Default,L,0,0,0,,你...你不去吗？ 开学典礼就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:12.06,Default,L,0,0,0,,没见过的新面孔呀 你是新生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:15.48,Default,L,0,0,0,,新月学园的校规十分严厉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:18.82,Default,L,0,0,0,,要是迟到了的话就进不去咯 直接退学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:20.82,Default,A,0,0,0,,我没有扫帚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:23.44,Default,A,0,0,0,,而且就算有也骑不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:26.28,Default,L,0,0,0,,抱歉 我要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:32.55,Default,L,0,0,0,,要坐上来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:37.36,Default,L,0,0,0,,我没试过载人 但是试试看说不定能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.36,0:09:39.50,Default,A,0,0,0,,真的吗 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:41.58,Default,A,0,0,0,,这世上也是有友善的魔女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:43.58,Default,A,0,0,0,,我叫卡嘉莉敦子 叫我亚可就行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:43.58,Comment,A,0,0,0,,{\pos(774,654)} Akko
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.09,0:09:46.09,Default,L,0,0,0,,我...我叫洛蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.09,0:09:46.09,Comment,L,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,654)}Lotte
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.09,0:09:47.88,Default,L,0,0,0,,赶快 我们没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:48.68,Default,A,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:51.74,Default,L,0,0,0,,那我们就出发咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:52.41,Default,A,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.16,0:09:54.84,Default,L,0,0,0,,飞吧 我的扫帚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:56.20,Default,L,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Tia Fraere
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:03.26,Default,A,0,0,0,,骗人 骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:05.14,Default,A,0,0,0,,飞了 飞了 飞了 飞...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:09.52,Default,L,0,0,0,,看起来行李有点太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:13.78,Default,L,0,0,0,,打开吧 前往新月学园的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:18.68,Default,A,0,0,0,,这是什么 这是什么 这是什么 这是什么！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:26.05,Default,A,0,0,0,,果然还是不行 不行 放我下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:27.70,Default,L,0,0,0,,稍微老实一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:33.42,Default,A,0,0,0,,行李...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:40.81,Default,S,0,0,0,,说到传说之森阿尔克图拉斯 寻常的魔女是无法进入的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:40.81,Comment,S,0,0,0,,{\pos(533,654)}Arcturus
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:40.81,TopLeft,,0,0,0,,Arcturus 即大角星 牧夫座的α星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:51.82,Default,L,0,0,0,,从来没有这样过 好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.16,0:10:54.36,Default,L,0,0,0,,难道说你带着盐吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:55.44,Default,A,0,0,0,,盐？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:58.61,Default,L,0,0,0,,灵脉讨厌盐分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:02.86,Default,A,0,0,0,,是这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:04.26,Default,L,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.61,0:11:05.54,Default,A,0,0,0,,梅干
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:06.57,Default,L,0,0,0,,快扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:09.53,Default,A,0,0,0,,我没有梅干就活不下去...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:11.86,Default,L,0,0,0,,求你了 快扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:13.86,Default,A,0,0,0,,我...我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:18.52,Default,A,0,0,0,,我的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.52,0:11:19.60,Default,L,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.94,0:11:25.85,Default,A,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.14,0:11:43.28,Default,U,0,0,0,,怎么了 阿尔克尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.14,0:11:43.28,Comment,U,0,0,0,,{\pos(701.714,654)}Alcor
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.14,0:11:43.28,TopLeft,U,0,0,0,,Alcor 北斗六的伴星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:02.62,Default,U,0,0,0,,难道说去了阿尔克图拉斯之森？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:23.93,Default,A,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:25.73,Default,A,0,0,0,,我的宝贝儿没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:31.12,Default,A,0,0,0,,死...死了..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:34.90,Default,S,0,0,0,,烦人透顶说的就是你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:36.46,Default,A,0,0,0,,还...还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.46,Default,S,0,0,0,,魔女不会这么简单的死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:42.13,Default,L,0,0,0,,洛蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:45.22,Default,A,0,0,0,,没事吧 没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:47.66,Default,L,0,0,0,,我没事 但是扫帚...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:51.24,Default,S,0,0,0,,看样子我们已经到了目的地了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:53.96,Default,A,0,0,0,,目的地？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:56.46,Default,A,0,0,0,,那...这里就是新月学园？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:57.34,Default,A,0,0,0,,开学典礼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:12:59.77,Default,L,0,0,0,,不是 这里只是陌生的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:10.81,Default,S,0,0,0,,阿尔克图拉斯之森
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:12.65,Default,L,0,0,0,,阿尔克图拉斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:15.10,Default,K,0,0,0,,不是吧 禁忌的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:16.28,Default,A,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.24,0:13:18.72,Default,L,0,0,0,,是在古老传说中的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:21.61,Default,L,0,0,0,,是被魔法树保护的神圣之地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:25.36,Default,L,0,0,0,,传说一旦被迷惑了 就算是魔女也很难逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:29.22,Default,A,0,0,0,,怎么这样 开学典礼要赶不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:32.29,Default,S,0,0,0,,不说这个 你说不定一生都会被困在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.48,0:13:35.05,Default,A,0,0,0,,我说 你别吓唬我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.99,0:13:39.74,Default,A,0,0,0,,找到我丢的行李了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:49.53,Default,L,0,0,0,,亚可 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:55.73,Default,L,0,0,0,,赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:58.69,Default,A,0,0,0,,那是什么鬼东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.44,Default,S,0,0,0,,是曼达拉草 食人植物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.44,Comment,S,0,0,0,,{\pos(580.571,654)}Mandrake
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:04.64,Default,S,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:20.50,Default,S,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:23.13,Default,A,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:23.97,Default,S,0,0,0,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:27.55,Default,S,0,0,0,,过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:29.12,Default,A,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:30.51,Default,S,0,0,0,,在这站好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:32.53,Default,S,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Juras Haras Haras
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:39.83,Default,A,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:41.40,Default,S,0,0,0,,念咒语
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:42.71,Default,A,0,0,0,,咒语？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:44.36,Default,L,0,0,0,,念的话就能找到回去的路吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:46.65,Default,S,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Kutchur Katela Flala.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:48.86,Default,A,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Kutchur Kat... F Fla fla?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:51.24,Default,S,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Kutchur Katela Flala!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:53.08,Default,S,0,0,0,,腹腔用力 大声念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:57.44,Default,A,0,0,0,,Kutchur Katela Flala!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:08.76,Default,A,0,0,0,,怎 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:24.59,Default,A,0,0,0,,你好~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:26.82,Default,A,0,0,0,,这是什么 刚才的咒语是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:30.49,Default,S,0,0,0,,意思是 「笨蛋 不服的话来吃掉我吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:31.28,Default,A,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:35.22,Default,S,0,0,0,,这是仅栖息在阿尔克图拉斯之森的传说中的鸡蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:35.22,Comment,S,0,0,0,,{\pos(994.286,654)}Cockatrice
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:38.25,Default,S,0,0,0,,据说羽毛上有着剧毒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:41.26,Default,S,0,0,0,,对于一个剧毒收藏家来说是超稀有的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:42.96,Default,S,0,0,0,,你们去吸引它的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:45.25,Default,S,0,0,0,,我会趁机去取得它的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:47.84,Default,A,0,0,0,,哈？ 也就是把我们当诱饵吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:49.63,Default,S,0,0,0,,不对 是祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:51.88,Default,S,0,0,0,,再念一遍刚才的「咒语」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.47,Default,A,0,0,0,,怎么可能念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:00.06,Default,S,0,0,0,,就是这样 小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:03.02,Default,S,0,0,0,,如果中了那家伙的吐息的话 会变成石头的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:04.27,Default,A,0,0,0,,石头？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:05.11,Default,A,0,0,0,,骗人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:19.74,Default,S,0,0,0,,到手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:30.42,Default,A,0,0,0,,停...停不下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:42.02,Default,A,0,0,0,,你还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:42.89,Default,L,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:45.10,Default,A,0,0,0,,我们得快点走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:48.95,Default,A,0,0,0,,再磨蹭的话 开学典礼要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.95,0:16:49.65,Default,L,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.64,0:16:52.28,Default,L,0,0,0,,我的脚...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:55.38,Default,L,0,0,0,,不行了 我们赶不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:56.74,Default,A,0,0,0,,没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:00.33,Default,A,0,0,0,,我绝不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:04.70,Default,A,0,0,0,,不能再逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:07.21,Default,A,0,0,0,,我要成为魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:11.05,Default,A,0,0,0,,如果向前伸手...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:13.92,Default,A,0,0,0,,就会一触即发
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:16.01,Default,A,0,0,0,,让人紧张的...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:18.47,Default,A,0,0,0,,令人兴奋的...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:21.37,Default,A,0,0,0,,只属于我的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:34.31,Default,A,0,0,0,,这是... 夏莉奥的魔杖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.59,Default,A,0,0,0,,洛蒂 躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:49.54,Default,L,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:57.09,Default,A,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Kutchur Katela Flala
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:17:59.14,Default,A,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:03.13,Default,A,0,0,0,,小鬼啊 看过来 向着拍手的声音来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:03.13,TopLeft,A,0,0,0,,日本儿童游戏中用来嘲讽的台词\N鬼さんこちら 手の鳴る方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:37.00,Default,A,0,0,0,,上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:38.09,Default,S,0,0,0,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:41.05,Default,S,0,0,0,,坐上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:49.21,Default,A,0,0,0,,谢谢 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.21,0:18:52.77,Default,S,0,0,0,,我叫苏西 苏西 曼芭芭拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.21,0:18:52.77,Comment,S,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,654)}Sucy      Manbavaran
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:55.08,Default,A,0,0,0,,谢谢 苏西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:04.80,Default,A,0,0,0,,真是难缠的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.80,0:19:07.16,Default,L,0,0,0,,载着三个人的话跑不掉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:11.67,Default,U,0,0,0,,不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:15.67,Default,A,0,0,0,,这次它喷火出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:20.22,Default,U,0,0,0,,她们为什么到这种地方来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:24.20,Default,A,0,0,0,,糟糕了 燃起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.32,0:19:28.64,Default,U,0,0,0,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:30.52,Default,U,0,0,0,,闪耀魔杖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:30.52,Comment,U,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,654)}Shiny Rod
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:32.27,Default,A,0,0,0,,好烫烫烫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:38.69,Default,U,0,0,0,,快念咒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:42.49,Default,U,0,0,0,,念出咒语
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:47.45,Default,A,0,0,0,,魔杖它...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:49.33,Default,U,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Noctu Orfei
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:52.54,Default,A,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Noctu... Orfei
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:53.63,Default,U,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Aude
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:55.52,Default,A,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Aude
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.53,0:19:58.21,Default,Bo,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Fraetor
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:05.43,Default,A,0,0,0,,闪耀魔箭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:05.43,Comment,A,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,654)}Shiny Arc
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,小家伙们 假期过得开心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在孕育了无数伟大魔女的历史悠久的我校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,今天起大家再次怀着自豪和礼节 又不忘谦逊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,全心投入对魔法的学习中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.77,0:21:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那么开学典礼现在开...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:34.31,Default,A,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.32,0:21:37.06,Default,A,0,0,0,,赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:39.16,Default,A,0,0,0,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:47.16,Default,T,0,0,0,,真是的 这可真是前所未闻的开学典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:50.87,Default,T,0,0,0,,你由于校长的特别许可的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:53.01,Default,T,0,0,0,,才被特许入学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.01,0:21:55.28,Default,T,0,0,0,,但愿你不要忘记这份恩情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.28,0:21:56.25,Default,A,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.94,0:22:00.76,Default,T,0,0,0,,和你的室友打声招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:11.14,Default,T,0,0,0,,从今天开始的三年里 你们三人会受到额外严厉的教导的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:17.14,Default,A,0,0,0,,我是卡嘉莉敦子 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.84,0:22:49.13,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}駈け出した日々に 行き着いたこの場所
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.13,0:22:53.75,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}触れた扉開いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.04,0:23:03.48,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}星空の彼方 夢の足跡 拾い集め歌うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.48,0:23:09.57,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}夢が駆けてく場所 今も心に秘めて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.57,0:23:19.64,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}夜を包み込む 魔法 掛けて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.64,0:23:24.62,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}踊りだす
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.84,0:23:29.88,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}焼きついたように 色づいた風景は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.88,0:23:34.35,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}転んだくらいじゃ 融けないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:35.88,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}世界は続くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.88,0:23:40.68,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}儚いままの今を 抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.68,0:23:48.17,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}変わらないまま 時間と光 見つめて歩いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.84,0:22:49.13,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}历经漫漫旅途 终于抵达于此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.13,0:22:53.75,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}轻轻推开门扉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.04,0:23:03.48,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}循着梦想的足迹 唱着歌走向星空的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.48,0:23:09.57,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}梦想的终点仍藏在心底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.57,0:23:19.64,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}施个魔咒 裹住夜色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.64,0:23:24.62,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}跳起舞来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.84,0:23:29.88,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}眼前的景色如在燃烧一般明亮绚丽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.88,0:23:34.35,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}那色彩即使跌倒也不会消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:35.88,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}世界依然继续运转呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.88,0:23:40.68,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}紧紧抱住这转瞬即逝的一刻
